description:
The Killer is tall, strong and tenacious. With only one loss, she is ranked 4th and looking to be the next rookie sensation. It's only her first year and she has already distinguished herself in a spectacular manner.
The Grapple is a seasoned veteran, a scrapper and a style point whore. If she gets control for even a second style points are a cummin'.
The winner of this great match up will in the Semi Finals and a member of the prestigious final four. Finally, she will go on to be in first ever live showing of US.
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE The Killer(4-1) Ranked 4th The Grappler(6-4) Ranked 5th
